<h3 id="get-vocabulary">Get Vocabulary</h3>
<p>нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳмқҙм§•мқ„ мң„н•ҙ л¬ём„ңлӮҙм—җ л“ұмһҘн•ң лӢЁм–ҙмқҳ л“ұмһҘнҡҹмҲҳк°Җ кё°лЎқлҗң <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dictionary</code>лҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳм—¬ лӢЁм–ҙ м§‘н•©мқё <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>лҘј л§Ңл“Өм–ҙм•ј н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">dictionary</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">{</span>
    <span class="s">'hug'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">10</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s">'pug'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">5</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s">'pun'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">12</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s">'bun'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">4</span><span class="p">,</span>
    <span class="s">'hugs'</span><span class="p">:</span><span class="mi">5</span>
<span class="p">}</span>

<span class="n">vocabulary</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">set</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">sum</span><span class="p">([</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">dictionary</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">keys</span><span class="p">()],[])))</span>
<span class="c1"># ['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>мң„ мҪ”л“ңлҠ” <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">dictionary</code>мқҳ лӢЁм–ҙл“Өмқ„ кө¬м„ұн•ҳлҠ” кёҖмһҗл“Өл§Ңмқ„ м¶”м¶ңн•ҳм—¬ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>м—җ м ҖмһҘн•ң мҪ”л“ңмһ…лӢҲлӢӨ. м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳ лӮҙм—җм„ң <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>лҘј мӮ¬мҡ©н•ҳкі  лӢӨмӢң м—…лҚ°мқҙнҠёлҘј л°ҳліөн•  кІғмһ…лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p>лӘЁл“  лӢЁм–ҙм—җ лҢҖн•ң bigram мҢҚмқ„ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pairs</code>лқјлҠ” л”•м…”л„ҲлҰ¬м—җ м ҖмһҘн•ҳл©ҙм„ң нҡҹмҲҳлҘј лҚ”н•ҙмӨҚлӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="kn">import</span> <span class="nn">collections</span>

<span class="n">pairs</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">collections</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">cnt</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">dictionary</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">():</span>
  <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">word_splited</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,[]</span> <span class="c1"># word_splitedлҠ” vocabularyм—җ мһҲлҠ” лӢЁм–ҙл“ӨлЎң wordлҘј л¶„лҰ¬н•ҳкі  м ҖмһҘн•©лӢҲлӢӨ
</span>  <span class="k">while</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
      <span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
      <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="mi">2</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
      <span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span>
      <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="mi">1</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">word2</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">zip</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">[:</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:]):</span>
  <span class="n">pairs</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">word1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="n">cnt</span>
 
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pairs</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">())</span>
<span class="c1"># dict_items([('hu', 15), ('ug', 20), ('pu', 17), ('un', 16), ('gs', 5), ('bu', 4)])
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">pairs</code>м—җм„ң к°ҖмһҘ л§Һмқҙ л“ұмһҘн•ң мҲңлҢҖлЎң м •л ¬ нӣ„ к°ҖмһҘ л§ҺмқҖ лӢЁм–ҙлҘј <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>м—җ м ҖмһҘн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">subword</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">sorted</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pairs</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">()),</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">lambda</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
<span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">subword</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># ['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's', 'ug']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>м—¬кё°к№Ңм§Җмқҳ кіјм •мқ„ л°ҳліөн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">_</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">range</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="mi">3</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="n">pairs</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">collections</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">defaultdict</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">int</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">cnt</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">dictionary</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">():</span>
        <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">word_splited</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,[]</span>
        <span class="k">while</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="o">&lt;</span><span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="mi">2</span>
            <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word1</span><span class="p">,</span><span class="n">word2</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="nb">zip</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">[:</span><span class="o">-</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">],</span><span class="n">word_splited</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">:]):</span>
            <span class="n">pairs</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">word1</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="n">word2</span><span class="p">]</span><span class="o">+=</span><span class="n">cnt</span>
    <span class="n">subword</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">sorted</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">pairs</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">items</span><span class="p">()),</span><span class="n">key</span><span class="o">=</span><span class="k">lambda</span> <span class="n">x</span> <span class="p">:</span> <span class="o">-</span><span class="n">x</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])[</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">][</span><span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">]</span>
    <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">subword</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># iter = 0
# [('ug', 20), ('pu', 17), ('un', 16), ('hu', 15), ('gs', 5), ('bu', 4)]
# ['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's', 'ug']
</span>
<span class="c1"># iter = 1
# [('un', 16), ('hug', 15), ('pu', 12), ('pug', 5), ('ugs', 5), ('bu', 4)]
# ['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's', 'ug', 'un']
</span>
<span class="c1"># iter = 2
