# ['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's', 'ug', 'un', 'hug']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>мқҙл ҮкІҢ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>мқё <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">['p', 'b', 'n', 'g', 'h', 'u', 's', 'ug', 'un', 'hug']</code>лҘј м–»мқ„ мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. corpusм—җм„ң к°ҖмһҘ л§Һмқҙ л“ұмһҘн•ң bigram мҢҚмқҙ мҲңм„ңлҢҖлЎң м¶”к°Җлҗҳм—ҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p>Huggingfaceмқҳ нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳмқҙм Җмқҳ кІҪмҡ° мқҙ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>к°Җ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocab.json</code>мңјлЎң м¶ңл Ҙлҗҳм–ҙ лӢЁм–ҙмҷҖ лӢЁм–ҙ мқёлҚұмҠӨ к°’мқҙ key-value нҳ•нғңлЎң м ҖмһҘлҗҳм–ҙ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<h3 id="tokenizing">Tokenizing</h3>
<p>нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳмқҙм§•мқ„ н•ҳл Өл©ҙ мң„м—җм„ң кө¬н•ң <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>к°Җ н•„мҡ”н•©лӢҲлӢӨ. <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>м—җ л”°лқј лӢЁм–ҙл“Өмқ„ лі‘н•©н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">UNK</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'&lt;unk&gt;'</span>
<span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'hugs'</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="k">while</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
        <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
    <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span>
    <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">UNK</span><span class="p">)</span>
    <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># ['h', 'ug', 's']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p><code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">&lt;unk&gt;</code> нҶ нҒ°мқҖ нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳмқҙм Җк°Җ <code class="language-plaintext highlighter-rouge">vocabulary</code>м—җ м—ҶлҠ” лӢЁм–ҙлҘј лҢҖмІҙн•  л•Ң мӮ¬мҡ©н•©лӢҲлӢӨ. мқҙлҹ° л¬ём ңлҘј OOV(Out of Vocabulary)лқј н•ҳлҠ”лҚ° м—¬кё°м„ңлҠ” corpusмқҳ нҒ¬кё°к°Җ нҒ¬м§Җ м•Ҡм•„ л°ңмғқн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<p>лӢӨмӢң лҸҢм•„мҷҖм„ң мң„мқҳ мҪ”л“ңлҠ” hugsлҘј h,u,g,sлЎң лӮҳлҲ„кі  h,ug,sлЎң лі‘н•©н•ҳлҠ” кіјм •мқҙм—ҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. мқҙ кіјм •мқ„ лҚ” мқҙмғҒ лі‘н•©н•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡмқ„ л•Ңк№Ңм§Җ л°ҳліөн•ҳм—¬ нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳмқҙм§•мқ„ мҲҳн–үн•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="s">'hugs'</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">while</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">:</span>
    <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
    <span class="k">while</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
        <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
        <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span>
        <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
            <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">UNK</span><span class="p">)</span>
        <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
      <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">:</span>
          <span class="k">break</span>
    <span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">r</span>
    <span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="c1"># ['h', 'ug', 's']
# ['hug', 's']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>мқҙ мҪ”л“ңлҘј н•ЁмҲҳлЎң м •мқҳн•ҳкі  л¬ёмһҘм—җ лҢҖн•ҙ нҶ нҒ¬лӮҳм•„м§•н•  мҲҳ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

<div class="language-python highlighter-rouge"><div class="highlight"><pre class="highlight"><code><span class="c1"># BPE Tokenizer
</span><span class="n">sentence</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'pug bug mug hug hugs'</span>
<span class="n">UNK</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="s">'&lt;unk&gt;'</span>

<span class="k">def</span> <span class="nf">word_tokenizing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">):</span>
    <span class="k">while</span> <span class="bp">True</span><span class="p">:</span>
        <span class="n">i</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="mi">0</span><span class="p">,</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
        <span class="k">while</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">):</span>
            <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="mi">1</span> <span class="o">&lt;</span> <span class="nb">len</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">)</span> <span class="ow">and</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="o">+</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="o">+</span><span class="mi">1</span><span class="p">])</span>
                <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
            <span class="k">elif</span> <span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">]</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">[</span><span class="n">i</span><span class="p">])</span>
            <span class="k">else</span><span class="p">:</span>
                <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">append</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">UNK</span><span class="p">)</span>
            <span class="n">i</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="mi">1</span>
          <span class="k">if</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">==</span> <span class="n">r</span><span class="p">:</span>
              <span class="c1"># лҚ”мқҙмғҒ лі‘н•©лҗҳм§Җ м•ҠлҠ”лӢӨл©ҙ мў…лЈҢ
</span>              <span class="k">break</span>
          <span class="n">word</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="n">r</span>
    <span class="k">return</span> <span class="n">word</span>

<span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">=</span> <span class="p">[]</span>
<span class="k">for</span> <span class="n">word</span> <span class="ow">in</span> <span class="n">sentence</span><span class="p">.</span><span class="n">split</span><span class="p">():</span>
    <span class="n">r</span> <span class="o">+=</span> <span class="n">word_tokenizing</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="nb">list</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">word</span><span class="p">),</span> <span class="n">vocabulary</span><span class="p">)</span>

<span class="k">print</span><span class="p">(</span><span class="n">r</span><span class="p">)</span>
<span class="c1"># ['p', 'ug', 'b', 'ug', '&lt;unk&gt;', 'ug', 'hug', 'hug', 's']
</span></code></pre></div></div>

<p>мқҙл ҮкІҢ BPE м•Ңкі лҰ¬мҰҳмқ„ нҶөн•ҙ subwordлҘј л¶„лҰ¬н•  мҲҳ мһҲм–ҙ н•©м„ұм–ҙлҘј мӮ¬м „м—җ нҸ¬н•Ён•ҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•„лҸ„ лҗҳлҠ” мһҘм җмқҙ мһҲмҠөлӢҲлӢӨ. лҳҗн•ң, мӮ¬м „м—җ лӢЁм–ҙк°Җ нҸ¬н•Ёлҗҳм§Җ м•Ҡм•„ л°ңмғқн•ҳлҠ” OOV(Out of vocabulary) л¬ём ңлҘј н•ҙкІ°н•ҳлҠ” л°©лІ•мқҙкё°лҸ„ н•©лӢҲлӢӨ.</p>

